verses.text: Then the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* said unto Moses , Now shalt thou see what I will do to Pharaoh : for with a strong hand shall he let them go , and with a strong hand shall he drive them out of his land.
And God spake unto Moses , and said unto him, I \add am\add* the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*:\f + \fr 6.2 \ft the \+nd LORD\+nd*: or, \+nd JEHOVAH\+nd*\f*
And I appeared unto Abraham , unto Isaac , and unto Jacob , by \add the name of\add* God Almighty , but by my name \nd \+w JEHOVAH|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* was I not known to them.
And I have also established my covenant with them, to give them the land of Canaan , the land of their pilgrimage , wherein they were strangers.
And I have also heard the groaning of the children of Israel , whom the Egyptians keep in bondage ; and I have remembered my covenant.

Wherefore say unto the children of Israel , I \add am\add* the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*, and I will bring you out from under the burdens of the Egyptians , and I will rid you out of their bondage , and I will redeem you with a stretched out arm , and with great judgments :

And I will take you to me for a people , and I will be to you a God : and ye shall know that I \add am\add* the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* your God , which bringeth you out from under the burdens of the Egyptians.

And I will bring you in unto the land , concerning the which I did swear to give it to Abraham , to Isaac , and to Jacob ; and I will give it you for an heritage : I \add am\add* the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*.\f + \fr 6.8 \ft swear: Heb. lift up my hand\f* \p
¶ And Moses spake so unto the children of Israel : but they hearkened not unto Moses for anguish of spirit , and for cruel bondage.\f + \fr 6.9 \ft anguish: Heb. shortness, or, straitness\f* \p
And the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* spake unto Moses , saying ,
Go in, speak unto Pharaoh king of Egypt , that he let the children of Israel go out of his land.

And Moses spake before the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*, saying , Behold, the children of Israel have not hearkened unto me; how then shall Pharaoh hear me , who \add am\add* of uncircumcised lips ?

And the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* spake unto Moses and unto Aaron , and gave them a charge unto the children of Israel , and unto Pharaoh king of Egypt , to bring the children of Israel out of the land of Egypt. \p
¶ These \add be\add* the heads of their fathers’ houses : The sons of Reuben the firstborn of Israel ; Hanoch , and Pallu , Hezron , and Carmi : these \add be\add* the families of Reuben.
And the sons of Simeon ; Jemuel , and Jamin , and Ohad , and Jachin , and Zohar , and Shaul the son of a Canaanitish woman : these \add are\add* the families of Simeon. \p

¶ And these \add are\add* the names of the sons of Levi according to their generations ; Gershon , and Kohath , and Merari : and the years of the life of Levi \add were\add* an hundred thirty and seven years.
The sons of Gershon ; Libni , and Shimi , according to their families.
And the sons of Kohath ; Amram , and Izhar , and Hebron , and Uzziel : and the years of the life of Kohath \add were\add* an hundred thirty and three years.
And the sons of Merari ; Mahali and Mushi : these \add are\add* the families of Levi according to their generations.
And Amram took him Jochebed his father’s sister to wife ; and she bare him Aaron and Moses : and the years of the life of Amram \add were\add* an hundred and thirty and seven years. \p
¶ And the sons of Izhar ; Korah , and Nepheg , and Zichri.
And the sons of Uzziel ; Mishael , and Elzaphan , and Zithri.
And Aaron took him Elisheba , daughter of Amminadab , sister of Naashon , to wife ; and she bare him Nadab , and Abihu , Eleazar , and Ithamar.
And the sons of Korah ; Assir , and Elkanah , and Abiasaph : these \add are\add* the families of the Korhites.

And Eleazar Aaron’s son took him \add one\add* of the daughters of Putiel to wife ; and she bare him Phinehas : these \add are\add* the heads of the fathers of the Levites according to their families.
These \add are\add* that Aaron and Moses , to whom the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* said , Bring out the children of Israel from the land of Egypt according to their armies.
These \add are\add* they which spake to Pharaoh king of Egypt , to bring out the children of Israel from Egypt : these \add are\add* that Moses and Aaron. \p
¶ And it came to pass on the day \add when\add* the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd* spake unto Moses in the land of Egypt ,

That the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d* spake unto Moses , saying , I \add am\add* the 
d \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*
d*: speak thou unto Pharaoh king of Egypt all that I say unto thee.
And Moses said before the \nd \+w LORD|strong="H3068"\+w*\nd*, Behold, I \add am\add* of uncircumcised lips , and how shall Pharaoh hearken unto me?
